<li><a href="http://news.giswiki.net/" class="external text" title="http://news.giswiki.net/" rel="nofollow">GISWiki.NEWS.Reader</a> - Searchable feed aggregator for a large collection of GIS news, mostly in English.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.nsgic.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.nsgic.org/" rel="nofollow">National States Geographic Information Council (NSGIC)</a></li>
