<li><a href="http://planetgs.com/" class="external text" title="http://planetgs.com/" rel="nofollow">Planet Geospatial</a> - feed aggregator for GIS related blogs.</li>
<li><a href="http://egsc.usgs.gov/isb/pubs/gis_poster/" class="external text" title="http://egsc.usgs.gov/isb/pubs/gis_poster/" rel="nofollow">USGS GIS Poster</a> — Frequently cited "What is GIS" poster.</li>
